mysql> SELECT c.CourseName, COUNT(s.StudentID) AS StudentCount
    -> FROM Students s
    -> JOIN Courses c ON s.CourseID = c.CourseID
    -> GROUP BY c.CourseName;
+-------------+--------------+
| CourseName  | StudentCount |
+-------------+--------------+
| History     |            6 |
| Mathematics |            7 |
| Science     |            7 |
+-------------+--------------+
3 rows in set (0.00 sec)

