| MaxPrice | MinPrice |
+----------+----------+
|  1000.00 |    40.00 |
+----------+----------+
1 row in set (0.00 sec)

mysql>
mysql> SELECT p.ProductName, SUM(s.Quantity) AS TotalQuantitySold
    -> FROM Sales s
    -> JOIN Products p ON s.ProductID = p.ProductID
    -> GROUP BY p.ProductName;
+--------------+-------------------+
| ProductName  | TotalQuantitySold |
+--------------+-------------------+
| External HDD |                 9 |
| Keyboard     |                19 |
| Laptop       |                 7 |
| Monitor      |                 8 |
| Mouse        |                15 |
| Printer      |                 4 |
| Router       |                 8 |
| Smartphone   |                11 |
| Tablet       |                10 |
| Webcam       |                 6 |
+--------------+-------------------+
10 rows in set (0.00 sec)

